headline: Weyerhaeuser to acquire 117,000 acres of timberlands in North Carolina, Virginia
summary: Weyerhaeuser (WY) announced an agreement to acquire approximately 117,000 acres of high-quality timberlands in North Carolina and Virginia from Roanoke Timberlands LLC, a subsidiary of Roseburg Forest Products, for $375M.
